{ The superior center makes the kingside expansion [#] } 22. h4 $1 { [%cal Yf7f6,Bh4h5] extremely difficult for Black to face. } ( 22. h3 $16 ) 22... Qa5 23. h5 ( 23. Ne2 $1 a3 24. b3 ) 23... a3 24. hxg6 hxg6 25. f5 gxf5 $2 ( { Perhaps Black could have still survived with } 25... axb2 $1 26. Qxb2 Ne5 27. Be2 Qa3 $1 ) 26. exf5 axb2 27. Qxb2 Ne5 28. Be2 Qc7 29. Qd2 Ra3 30. Nc2 Bh6 31. Qxh6 Rxc3 32. Bh5 Rf8 33. Rxe5 { [%csl Gc5,Gf8][%cal Gd6e5,Gf2c5,Gh6f8] } 33... fxe5 34. Rxd6 { [%cal Rd6g6] } 34... Bxf5 35. Bxc5 Bxc2 36. Qxf8+ { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0
