{ Another demonstration of the space advantage is presented by Petrosian: } 16. Bxc5 $1 dxc5 { By giving his strong bishop for the knight, White managed to achieve a better pawn structure. He can now exploit the mobile central majority. } 17. e5 { [%csl Ge5,Gf4,Gg4][%cal Gd2e4,Gd1d8] } 17... Nd7 18. Nde4 Qc7 19. Rd3 Nb6 20. b3 Rad8 21. Rfd1 { White has complete domination. } 21... Be7 22. g5 Nc8 23. Qh5 Rxd3 24. Rxd3 Rd8 25. Nf6+ { The final touch, Petrosian has a winning attack now. } 25... gxf6 26. Rh3 Kf8 27. Qxh7 Ke8 28. g6 Bf8 29. g7 Bxg7 30. Qxg7 Qe7 31. Ne4 Rd1+ 32. Kf2 f5 33. Nf6+ Kd8 34. Rh8+ { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0
