1. e4 d6 2. d4 Nf6 3. Nc3 e5 { Bonus line. A plan against the aggressive } 4. f4 exd4 5. Qxd4 Nc6 { The main plan is to orientate to a successful central break as usual with d6-d5! } 6. Bb5 Bd7 7. Bxc6 ( 7. Qf2 ) 7... Bxc6 8. Nf3 ( 8. Nge2 Qe7 9. Ng3 Nxe4 $1 10. Ngxe4 f5 11. O-O fxe4 12. Re1 Qf6 13. Qc4 O-O-O $15 ) 8... Be7 ( 8... g6 9. Bd2 Bg7 10. O-O-O O-O 11. Qd3 Re8 12. Rhe1 b5 $36 ) ( 8... Nxe4 $1 9. Nxe4 Qe7 10. Kf2 Bxe4 11. Re1 ( 11. Nd2 d5 12. Nxe4 dxe4 13. Be3 Qe6 $15 ) 11... d5 12. Ng5 f5 13. Nxe4 dxe4 ) 9. Be3 O-O 10. O-O-O Ng4 11. Rhe1 Bf6 12. Qc4 Bxc3 13. Qxc3 Qf6 14. e5 dxe5 ( 14... Qh6 $5 15. exd6 Nxe3 16. Qxe3 cxd6 ) 15. fxe5 Qe6 16. Bc5 Rfd8 17. Kb1 Bxf3 ( { Missing } 17... Rxd1+ $1 18. Rxd1 Qf5 { with the idea to meet } 19. h3 ( { Better is } 19. Nd4 Qd7 $11 ) 19... Bxf3 20. gxf3 Nxe5 $17 ) 18. gxf3 Nxe5 19. Rxd8+ Rxd8 20. b3 f6 21. f4 b6 22. Bb4 a5 23. Bxa5 bxa5 24. fxe5 fxe5 25. Qxa5 e4 26. Qxc7 Re8 27. Re3 Qd5 28. Qc3 h5 29. h4 Rf8 30. Rg3 Rf7 31. a4 Qd6 32. Re3 Rc7 33. Qe1 Qc6 34. Qe2 { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0
